item.title: wtf i am sick again..
item.description: However.. this time is a lot more pleasant. All I do is get tired when I run over 1 mile and sleep when I lay in my bed. oh.. and I also have the sniffles. but I am going to take some medicine.. and a E-merge-ENC-E. it will be a nice cocktail.So us IT workers have been complaining to the building manager that we need mountain dew in our damned pop machine.
